I really hope this cover is lying and they won’t kill Gwen’s bandmates.

summary: Okay so my birthday is on April 16 and I've been really sour about Endgame not releasing on my birthday and I have my French...
body:
Avengers: Endgame

Okay so my birthday is on April 16 and I’ve been really sour about Endgame not releasing on my birthday and I have my French finals tomorrow but I’m lying here in bed thinking about how 26th April could possibly be better than 16th April and I was crunching the numbers and oh my holy fucking gods…

26/04/2019

First four digits - 2+6+0+4 = 12

Last four digits - 2+0+1+9 = 12

What. In. The. Actual. Fuck.

Okay so my birthday is on April 16 and I’ve been really sour about Endgame not releasing on my birthday and I have my French finals tomorrow but I’m lying here in bed thinking about how 26th April could possibly be better than 16th April and I was crunching the numbers and oh my holy fucking gods…

26/04/2019

First four digits - 2+6+0+4 = 12

Last four digits - 2+0+1+9 = 12

What. In. The. Actual. Fuck.

FRIENDLY NEIGHBORHOOD SPIDER-MAN #6
TOM TAYLOR (W) • Yildiray Cinar (A) • Cover by ANDREW C. ROBINSON
MARVEL BATTLE LINES VARIANT COVER BY NEXON
• The neighborhood, and the planet, is doomed. Spider-Man is powerless to stop the end of the world. Only Earth’s Newest and Mightiest Hero, Spider-Bite, can save the day.
• Wait, WHAT?!
32 PGS./Rated T …$3.99

Holy shit, a Marvel May book that isn’t a tie-in to fucking War of the Realms? MUST BE A FUCKING MIRACLE!
